(to awe the Three Realms.)

52
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:40,290
(Nowadays...)

53
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:42,140
(East Sea Dragon Palace)

54
00:03:42,170 --> 00:03:43,080
Elder Dragon King.

55
00:03:43,210 --> 00:03:45,790
The war between the Gods
and the Asuras grows fiercer by the day.

56
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:48,500
I'm afraid it will soon spread
to Dragon Clan.

57
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:50,965
