The one fighting the Asuras this time

58
00:03:50,989 --> 00:03:52,337
(Manluo)
is the God of Light Soul.

59
00:03:52,410 --> 00:03:55,110
(Ao Lei, South Sea Dragon King)
The Shadow Gods are not involved.

60
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:56,830
