(Ao Guang, East Sea Dragon King)
Nonsense!

68
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:13,330
The Golden Soul of the Dragon
is the bloodline of our ancestors!

69
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:14,790
This matter is not up for discussion.

70
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:15,870
Guang.

71
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:18,530
Opposing the Shadows

72
00:04:18,650 --> 00:04:21,170
will only bring annihilation
upon the Dragon Clan.

73
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:22,440
Silence!

74
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:24,670
If you dare side with the Shadows,

75
00:04:24,670 --> 00:04:26,020
I will kill you myself!

76
00:04:27,330 --> 00:04:29,600
Useless old fool.

77
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,032
(Ao Yilong)
Ao Yilong.

78
00:04:31,056 --> 00:04:31,870
(Son of the South Sea Dragon King)
Die!

79
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:32,790
You…

80
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:44,040
How dare you…

81
