Send the order.

82
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:11,870
Mobilize the entire army.

83
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:34,140
(Ao Jiao, East Sea Crown Prince)

84
00:05:36,580 --> 00:05:38,170
Why does Father suddenly want to see me?

85
00:05:39,290 --> 00:05:40,470
(Ao Ye, Son of the East Sea Dragon King)
He…

86
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:42,330
