89
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,870
Where is Father?

90
00:05:56,210 --> 00:05:56,860
He's...

91
00:05:57,150 --> 00:05:58,060
He's just up ahead.

92
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,910
Release the arrows!

93
00:06:31,060 --> 00:06:32,930
(East Sea Third Uncle)

94
00:06:40,210 --> 00:06:40,910
Guang.

95
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:42,250
Darn it.

96
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:43,170
Kill him!

97
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:59,080
I am not here today to kill.

98
00:06:59,090 --> 00:07:01,080
Those who surrender
to the Celestial Dragon Realm

99
00:07:01,090 --> 00:07:01,790
will be spared.

100
00:07:01,790 --> 00:07:05,500
