Elder Dragon King.

101
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:07,830
Prince Ao Jiao will never let you go!

102
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:09,040
Ao Jiao?

103
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:12,600
I've already arranged for father and son
to reunite in the underworld.

104
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,520
Wretched old thief of the South Sea!

105
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:23,040
You traitor.

106
00:07:29,450 --> 00:07:30,770
It's Crown Prince Ao Jiao.

107
00:07:31,290 --> 00:07:32,960
Ao Jiao.

108
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:36,330
Do you think I'm dead?

109
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,370
Your Highness.

110
00:07:45,670 --> 00:07:46,420
Father.

111
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,080
South Sea.

112
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,460
