of the Red Flame wants is on Ao Jiao.

125
00:09:46,580 --> 00:09:47,120
Hurry!

126
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:49,120
Father.

127
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:50,420
From now on,

128
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:51,960
the lives of the Dragon Clan

129
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:53,670
will be decided by you.

130
00:09:54,170 --> 00:09:55,000
Shut up!

131
00:09:55,500 --> 00:09:57,580
The Shadows are our heaven.

132
00:09:58,250 --> 00:10:01,920
We're just doing their work.

133
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:05,040
Uncle.

134
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:07,330
Both you and the Shadows are heaven.

135
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:08,710
Please spare

136
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:10,790
Ao Ye's life.

137
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:13,120
To show loyalty,

138
00:10:13,330 --> 00:10:13,670
I…

139
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:17,040
I'm willing to cut off my dragon horn!

140
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:24,250
Useless eyesore.

141
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:25,830
I'll kill you!

142
00:10:25,830 --> 00:10:26,500
Wait.

143
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:29,330
He still has a use.

144
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:32,830
Send the good news
to the Shadow Gods first.

145
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,420
Yes!

146
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:35,040
Father.

147
00:10:35,460 --> 00:10:36,580
Then this East Sea...

148
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:40,170
You handle it within three days.

149
