151
00:11:20,850 --> 00:11:23,180
(North Sea Dragon Palace)

152
00:11:33,850 --> 00:11:34,955
(Ao Bing, Princess of the North Sea)

153
00:11:34,979 --> 00:11:36,060
(Ao Shun, North Sea Dragon King)

154
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:38,370
The newly appointed
East Sea Dragon King,

155
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:40,710
