163
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,490
I hope the North Sea will send troops

164
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,000
to join me in punishing the South Sea.

165
00:12:06,420 --> 00:12:07,830
I cannot interfere

166
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:09,330
your internal matters.

167
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:10,790
Go back.

168
00:12:11,380 --> 00:12:13,250
