173
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:28,790
Such a hassle.

174
00:12:28,790 --> 00:12:29,920
You go back first.

175
00:12:30,380 --> 00:12:31,830
Let me think it over.

176
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:44,500
Darn it.

177
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,870
