keeps shirking.

178
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:49,710
The North Sea Dragon Clan
lives apart from the world.

179
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:51,740
Even when the Dragon Clan
faces foreign invasions,

180
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,460
