181
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,500
and avoid conflict.

182
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:56,420
So spineless!

183
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:57,040
Shut up!

184
00:12:57,700 --> 00:12:59,170
Don't slander the North Sea like that!

185
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,120
She is...

186
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:04,710
The Princess of the North Sea!

187
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,530
Your Highness.

188
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:14,290
What I just said was out of line.

189
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:15,660
If it offended you,

190
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,290
