191
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:22,710
The North Sea has no cowards.

192
00:13:23,290 --> 00:13:25,000
We just don't fight unwinnable battles.

193
00:13:25,290 --> 00:13:26,080
I want to see

194
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:28,120
