211
00:15:30,920 --> 00:15:33,920
These are high-quality
Soul of the Dragon offered to you.

212
00:15:35,170 --> 00:15:36,000
(Nezha, Great God of the Red Flame)
High-quality?

213
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:45,870
And the legendary Golden Dragon Soul?

214
00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:48,860
No news yet?

215
00:15:50,630 --> 00:15:51,500
Great God!

216
00:15:51,740 --> 00:15:52,470
Great God!

217
00:15:53,170 --> 00:15:54,250
Spare my life!

218
00:15:55,290 --> 00:15:57,710
