to be buried with Qing.

239
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:14,500
Take him down.

240
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:15,670
Go!

241
00:17:34,410 --> 00:17:35,330
Nezha.

242
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:37,513
(Primordial Jade Lord)
Use the power I granted

243
00:17:37,537 --> 00:17:38,750
(Primordial Jade Lord)
