244
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:41,460
Find the bloodline
of the Golden Dragon Soul.

245
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:43,830
Then you can resurrect your beloved.

246
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:46,420
From today onwards,

247
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:48,110
