248
00:17:48,130 --> 00:17:49,690
Only the Red Flame.

249
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:54,500
(I will definitely find
the Golden Dragon Soul)

250
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:56,420
(and let you be reborn.)

